50
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,600
What are you doing?

51
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,519
I think we need to visit Uncle Bao again.

52
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,439
You dare go back?

53
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,120
We were kicked out yesterday.

54
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,759
San Yatou violated the Ghost Opera Troupe's taboo.

55
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,279
What do you think about that?

56
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,879
The Ghost Opera Troupe...

57
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,879
isn't it just some mystifying trickery?

58
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,959
I don't believe in any retribution.

59
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,360
You mean...

60
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:26,319
San Yatou's death...

61
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,360
has nothing to do with the Ghost Opera Troupe?

62
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:29,480
Exactly.

63
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,439
This is definitely not that simple.

64
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,560
I examined San Yatou's body.

65
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,600
She had obvious injuries.

66
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,040
What about Uncle Bao?

67
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,639
He must be hiding something.

68
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:40,959
Let's go.

69
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:42,079
Let's go take a look.

70
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,360
Uncle Bao?

71
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,680
Uncle Bao?

72
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:09,439
Uncle Bao?

73
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,600
We're coming in.

74
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,560
Uncle Bao!

75
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:25,279
Uncle Bao!

76
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,680
Who did this?

77
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,639
Uncle Bao...

78
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:53,160
He chose to leave on his own.

79
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,560
My girl...

80
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,399
You know our family's situation.

81
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,680
I don't want you to suffer with me.

82
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,439
This Young Master Lai...

83
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,839
is rich and powerful.

84
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,079
And he's taken a liking to you.

85
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:16,360
If you marry over there...

86
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,199
you'll surely enjoy a good life.

87
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,639
Dad...

88
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,000
what kind of person he is...

89
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,240
you know perfectly well.

90
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:25,040
Isn't this pushing me into a fire pit?

91
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,720
That they took a liking to you

92
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,800
is your good fortune.

93
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,839
You should be content.

94
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,480
Did you smoke opium again?

95
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,199
Did you?

96
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:37,360
You smoked away all the family's money.

97
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:39,240
And now you want to sell your daughter.

98
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,560
Are you even human?

99
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:41,680
If anyone's marrying, you do it.

100
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,040
I definitely won't marry.

101
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,959
This marriage...

102
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,920
You will marry whether you want to

103
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,120
or not.

104
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:00,680
Madam Lai.

105
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,720
Young Master Lai.

106
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,600
My daughter is a bit shy.

107
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:05,399
She's afraid to see people.

108
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,720
It doesn't matter.

109
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:10,600
A Pure maiden who has yet to get married

110
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,600
shouldn't be seen by just anyone.

111
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,040
Then this marriage...

112
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,360
we have settled it.

113
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,560
It's settled.

114
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,160
Then your son-in-law

115
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:23,120
will come to ask for her hand in a few days.

116
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,399
Father-in-law.

117
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,560
Please accept this money.

118
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,519
Once related to our Lai Family,

119
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,759
you won't worry about food or clothing.

120
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,480
You'll have wealth and honor.

121
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,600
Of course.

122
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,399
Of course.

123
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,159
Yatou.

124
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,039
Yatou.

125
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:00,559
Yatou.

126
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:06,559
You accepted the Bride price.

127
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:08,200
And now you tell me there's no one here?

128
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,000
Do you take my Lai Family for fools?

129
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,320
Young Master Lai.

130
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:13,200
My daughter is still young.

131
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,399
She acted on impulse.

132
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:16,440
I'll go find her for you right now, okay?

133
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,480
Find her now?

134
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:19,639
So you father and daughter can run away together?

135
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,000
Young Master Lai.

136
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,600
I wouldn't dare!

137
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,799
We are in-laws now.

138
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:25,480
How could I deceive you?

139
00:09:25,759 --> 00:09:26,679
Screw you.

140
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,919
You think you're worthy of being in-laws with our Lai Family?

141
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,480
If we hadn't taken a liking to your girl,

142
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,960
how many lifetimes would it take for you

143
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,799
to have any connection with our Lai Family?

144
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:35,399
I gave you plenty for the Bride price.

145
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,639
If I don't see her,

146
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:37,840
I'll take your life.

147
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:40,120
Go.

148
00:09:40,279 --> 00:09:41,159
Catch her and bring her back to me.

149
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:41,720
Yes.

150
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,080
Screw you!

151
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,120
Stop hitting him!

152
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:54,440
What is going on here?

153
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:55,240
Young Master.

154
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:57,080
She was like this when we brought her back from Changxian Temple.

155
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,480
I heard that place is spooky.

156
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,480
She probably encountered something unclean.

157
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:04,879
Like this, she wants to enter our Lai Family's door?

158
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,120
I'm telling you.

159
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,120
Hurry up and pay back the money you owe the Lai Family.

160
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,200
Or else I'll take your life.

161
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:10,919
