162
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,799
Young Master Lai, I beg you.

163
00:10:12,799 --> 00:10:14,320
I have no money, Young Master Lai.

164
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,279
Screw you.

165
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,320
Let's go.

166
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:16,720
This...

167
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:24,279
