00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,639
Where is my money?

172
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,519
Where is my money?

173
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,159
Where's the money?

174
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,320
I'll be back later.

175
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,840
Just a few more puffs.

176
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:20,480
Yatou.

177
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:22,720
